cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.CY, cs.SI 

This paper focuses on the interaction between pedestrians and automated vehicles, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and robotics (cs.RO). The experiment also collected gaze information, which suggests the use of computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the timing of communication, which could be related to cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
